query:
SELECT s.id, s.name, s.email, a.id as anamnesis_id, a.objective, a.experience_level, a.training_frequency, a.restrictions 
FROM students s 
LEFT JOIN anamnesis a ON s.id = a.student_id 
WHERE s.name ILIKE '%Laura%' 
LIMIT 5;
